Only a 2.5A power supply is needed, if not using USB port. Similar models from D-Link, which do not feature USB port, come with 2.5A AC adapter.
"21514AV11C1*1A1" "AV11C1 REV.A1" is silkscreened on WI1 board top.
"DIR-635A1 Rev:A1" "21514DR635A11A1" is silkscreened on system board top.
Full-speed USB transceiver is Sipex 5301CY ==Images== File:DIR-625revA1.label bottom.jpeg File:DIR-625revA1.board top.jpeg File:DIR-625revA1.wi top.jpeg [[Has images::internal| ]]
